data.title: Opportunity for bands to perform at Teenage Kicks in Shrewsbury
data.meta_description: Teenage Kicks will be returning to the Quarry this summer with the involvement of the Hive Music and Media Centre. Local bands and young musicians are being given the chance to perform at the popular event, which will be taking place on June 23.
